{"tid":553490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（流感）兩歲支那童，黎香港搶醫療資源。","createTime":"2018-02-07T13:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T23:47:47.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5de9780987a5a3f74d9a1d757006ebeffb5e7261","tid":553490,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"到傍晚，衞生防護中心公佈另一宗兒童嚴重流感個案，患者是一名長居於北京的兩歲香港男童。中心指，該名男童於2月2日起出現發燒、咳嗽和流鼻水等病徵，翌日起更出現行為異常，5日起出現身體抽搐，至昨日（6日）被家人帶回香港到瑪麗醫院求醫，臨床診斷為乙流併發腦病變"},{"pid":"ff51e9013179a9acdc3524132bd21fd44284f9ba","tid":553490,"uid":29314,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"香港既醫療資源就係畀呢班支那種搶晒！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲想我地捐血？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦！"},{"pid":"d7ec65545658e7e8cb4917b45bb3ff813f87c44d","tid":553490,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e026cd76656f71b8c3a21eb7667adaea0e340534","tid":553490,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:46:59.000Z","msg":"早登極樂"},{"pid":"b551af1b5b1646a605ee1ecec997d319ea98cb02","tid":553490,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:47:47.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}